landfill of Edo city waste, which led to the creation of the island now known as {{ill|Eidaijima|ja|永代島|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Xianfeng|ja|咸豊|ko|함풍|uk|Сяньфен|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1853]] {{ill|May 6|ja|5月6日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – During the Taiping Rebellion, Hong Xiuquan entered Nanjing, renaming it Tianjing and establishing it as the capital of the Taiping Heavenly Kingdom.
== Births == * [[Ōei]] 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1401]] {{ill|May 12|ja|5月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Shōkō Tennō|ja|称光天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 101st Emperor of Japan (died [[1428]]). * {{ill|Hōreki|ja|宝暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1762]] {{ill|April 23|ja|4月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Iizuka Iga-shichi|ja|飯塚伊賀七|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, an inventor (died [[1836]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1828]] {{ill|May 12|ja|5月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hirano Kunomi|ja|平野国臣|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a retainer of the Fukuoka Domain (died [[1864]]).
== Deaths == * [[Shitō]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[997]] {{ill|May 8|ja|5月8日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Taizong of Song|ja|太宗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 2nd Emperor of the Song dynasty (born [[939]]).
