* {{ill|Kōan|ja|康安}} 1st year / {{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平}} 16th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[1361]] {{ill|May 4|ja|5月4日}}) – The Northern Court changed its era name from {{ill|Enbun|ja|延文}} to {{ill|Kōan|ja|康安}}.
* {{ill|Tenna|ja|天名}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1683]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日}}) – "Yaoya Oshichi" was executed by immolation at Suzukamori Prison.
