{{Lunisolar March|qq=}} '''March 29''' is the 29th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. If the month is {{Nihongo|Small|小|qq=}} then this is the last day of the month. Otherwise if the month is {{Nihongo|Big|大|qq=}} then it is the second last day.<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20250111081847/https://www.chinaknowledge.de/History/Terms/calendar.html</ref><ref>https://www.nippon.com/en/japan-glances/jg00122/the-japanese-calendar.html</ref> Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Chōkan|ja|長寛|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1163]] {{ill|May 4|ja|5月4日|qq=}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Ōhō|ja|応保|qq=}} to {{ill|Chōkan|ja|長寛|qq=}}. * {{ill|Kōan|ja|康安|qq=}} 1st year / {{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平|qq=}} 16th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1361]] {{ill|May 4|ja|5月4日|qq=}}) – The Northern Court changed its era name from {{ill|Enbun|ja|延文|qq=}} to {{ill|Kōan|ja|康安|qq=}}. * {{ill|Tenna|ja|天名|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1683]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=}}) – "Yaoya Oshichi" was executed by immolation at Suzukamori Prison. * {{ill|Genroku|ja|元禄|qq=}} 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1696]] {{ill|April 30|ja|4月30日|qq=}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate permitted landfill of Edo city waste, which led to the creation of the island now known as {{ill|Eidaijima|ja|永代島|qq=}}. * {{ill|Xianfeng|ja|咸豊|ko|함풍|uk|Сяньфен|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1853]] {{ill|May 6|ja|5月6日|qq=}}) – During the Taiping Rebellion, Hong Xiuquan entered Nanjing, renaming it Tianjing and establishing it as the capital of the Taiping Heavenly Kingdom.
== Births == * [[Ōei]] 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[1401]] {{ill|May 12|ja|5月12日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Shōkō Tennō|ja|称光天皇|qq=}}, the 101st Emperor of Japan (died [[1428]]). * {{ill|Hōreki|ja|宝暦|qq=}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1762]] {{ill|April 23|ja|4月23日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Iizuka Iga-shichi|ja|飯塚伊賀七|qq=}}, an inventor (died [[1836]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1828]] {{ill|May 12|ja|5月12日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hirano Kunomi|ja|平野国臣|qq=}}, a retainer of the Fukuoka Domain (died [[1864]]).
== Deaths == * [[Shitō]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} [[997]] {{ill|May 8|ja|5月8日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Taizong of Song|ja|太宗|qq=}}, the 2nd Emperor of the Song dynasty (born [[939]]).
