== Births == * [[Ōei]] 8th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1401|1401]] [[:en:May 12|May 12]]) – [[:en:Emperor Shōkō|Shōkō Tennō]], the 101st Emperor of Japan (died [[:en:1428|1428]]). * [[:en:Hōreki|Hōreki]] 12nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1762]] [[:en:April 23|April 23]]) – {{ill|Iizuka Iga-shichi|ja|飯塚伊賀七|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iizuka Iga-shichi|qq=}}, an inventor (died [[1836]]). * [[:en:Bunsei|Bunsei]] 11th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1828]] [[:en:May 12|May 12]]) – {{ill|Hirano Kunomi|ja|平野国臣|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hirano Kunomi|qq=}}, a retainer of the Fukuoka Domain (died [[1864]]).
== Deaths == * [[Shitō]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[997]] [[:en:May 8|May 8]]) – [[:en:Thái Tông|Taizong of Song]], the 2nd Emperor of the Song dynasty (born [[939]]).
